                <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="2"/>et memoriae Antistiae Firmi<lb break="no" n="3"/>ne co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>iugi</abbr></expan> rarissime quae vixit <lb n="4"/>mecum <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> XXIII Malius Secundus <lb n="5"/>b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> maritus f&amp;lt;e&amp;gt;cit me poni </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> εἴ τις ἐν τούτῳ τῷ ἡρῴῳ ὅπου κεῖτε <lb n="2"/>ἡ προγεγραμμένη θελήσι ἄλλον <lb n="3"/>ἕτερον θεῖναι δώσι τῷ ταμίῳ |(δηνάρια) βφʹ <lb n="4"/>καὶ τῇ Ὀδησσειτῶν πόλι |(δηνάρια) βφʹ
            </ab></div></div>
